                                                                                                                                                             Lists
   I - Lists Tags : 
       1 - Unordered Lists : (<ul>).
       2 - Ordered Lists : (<ol>).
       		attribute 							values
       		type : Type of Numbering 				"1" (default), "a", "A", "i", "I"
       		start : Start from a specific number
       		reversed: Reverses the numbering
       		value : specific value for an item
       3 - Description Lists : (<dl>).
       4 - List Item : (<li>).
       
   II - Example : same as <ol>
     <ul>
         <li>Item 1</li>
         <li>Item 2</li>
         <li>Item 3</li>
     </ul>
